## About this package

This package provides the CUDA NVRTC (runtime compilation) component v${EMGU_CUDA_NVRTC_VERSION}.

This package provides the native NVRTC dependencies for EMGU software libraries. It is used by cuDNN's
runtime-fusion engine to JIT-compile fused kernels at runtime; without it cuDNN falls back to its
precompiled engines.

For for information, please visit
<${NUGET_EMGU_URL}/wiki>

